Package org.jboss.windup.config.parser

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ElementHandler<T>
    Parses the given Element and returns a result, that will depend upon the underlying implementation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HandlerId
    Identifies an ElementHandler by its tag name and namespace.
    ParserContext
    Handles maintaining the list of handlers associated with each tag/namespace pair, as well as selecting the right handler for element.
    TechnologyReferenceAliasTranslatorHandler
    This produces a list of TechnologyReferenceAliasTranslator objects.
    XMLLabelProviderLoader
    Searches for and loads LabelProviders from XML files.
    XMLRuleProviderLoader
    This RuleProviderLoader searches for and loads AbstractRuleProviders from XML files that within all addons, with filenames that end in ".windup.xml" or ".rhamt.xml".
    XMLTechnologyMetadataLoader  
    XMLTechnologyReferenceAliasTranslatorLoader
    Implements a TechnologyReferenceAliasTranslatorLoader using xml files.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    WindupXMLRulesetParsingException
    Exception thrown when parsing of the ruleset failed.

    Annotation Type Description
